---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kuis Pramuka Interaktif" description="Latihan kepramukaan online: Morse, Semaphore, Sandi, SKU, Kompas, P3K, Simpul, Dasa Darma, dan 16 modul lainnya. Gratis, offline, kumpulkan XP dan lencana.">
	<div class="dashboard">

		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="hero glass-card">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<span class="hero-tag">Gugus Depan Online</span>
				<h1 id="hero-heading">Siap Menguji Kemampuan Kepramukaanmu?</h1>
				<p>Asah kemampuan Morse, Semaphore, Sandi, dan SKU dalam kuis interaktif yang seru. Kumpulkan XP, naikkan level, dan raih Lencana Pandu Tertinggi!</p>
				<div class="hero-actions">
					<a href="#kategori-kuis" class="btn btn-gold">Mulai Petualangan 🧭</a>
					<button id="btn-reset-data" class="btn btn-secondary">Reset Progres</button>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-deco">
				<svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="compass-svg">
					<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" stroke="var(--color-gold)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="3 3"/>
					<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="37" stroke="var(--color-primary-light)" stroke-width="1" fill="none" opacity="0.4"/>
					<line x1="50" y1="10" x2="50" y2="90" stroke="var(--color-primary-light)" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.3"/>
					<line x1="10" y1="50" x2="90" y2="50" stroke="var(--color-primary-light)" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.3"/>
					<path d="M50 14 L54 50 L50 86 L46 50 Z" fill="var(--color-gold)" opacity="0.9"/>
					<path d="M50 14 L50 50 L46 50 Z" fill="var(--color-gold-light)"/>
					<path d="M14 50 L50 54 L86 50 L50 46 Z" fill="var(--color-primary-light)" opacity="0.7"/>
					<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="4" fill="var(--color-bg)" stroke="var(--color-gold)" stroke-width="2"/>
					<text x="50" y="8" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6" fill="var(--color-primary-light)" opacity="0.5" font-family="Outfit">U</text>
					<text x="50" y="97" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6" fill="var(--color-primary-light)" opacity="0.5" font-family="Outfit">S</text>
					<text x="5" y="52" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6" fill="var(--color-primary-light)" opacity="0.5" font-family="Outfit">B</text>
					<text x="95" y="52" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6" fill="var(--color-primary-light)" opacity="0.5" font-family="Outfit">T</text>
				</svg>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Stats Grid -->
		<section class="stats-grid">
			<div class="stat-card glass-card">
				<div class="stat-icon xp-color">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
						<path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-info">
					<span class="stat-label">Total Pengalaman</span>
					<h2 id="stats-xp-val" class="stat-value">0 XP</h2>
					<p class="stat-sub">Jawab soal dengan benar untuk XP</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="stat-card glass-card">
				<div class="stat-icon level-color">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
						<path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-info">
					<span class="stat-label">Peringkat Pandu</span>
					<h2 id="stats-level-val" class="stat-value">Level 1</h2>
					<p id="stats-rank-title" class="stat-sub">Pandu Mula</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="stat-card glass-card">
				<div class="stat-icon badges-color">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
						<path d="M12 15L15.5 18L14.5 13.5L18 10.5L13.5 10L12 5.5L10.5 10L6 10.5L9.5 13.5L8.5 18L12 15Z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-info">
					<span class="stat-label">Lencana Diperoleh</span>
					<h2 id="stats-badges-val" class="stat-value">0 / 34</h2>
					<p class="stat-sub">Buka kunci lencana pencapaian</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Quiz Categories -->
		<section id="kategori-kuis" class="categories-section">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>Pilih Modul Latihan</h2>
				<p>16 modul latihan dalam 3 kelompok kompetensi kepramukaan.</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Kelompok 1: Komunikasi & Isyarat -->
			<div class="cat-group-header">
				<div class="cat-group-icon comm-group">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3>Komunikasi &amp; Isyarat</h3>
					<span class="cat-group-count">3 modul</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="categories-grid">
				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon morse-bg">
							<span>• — — •</span>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag easy">Mudah – Sedang</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Morse (Telegraf Hutan)</h3>
						<p>Terjemahkan kode titik dan garis Morse menjadi huruf/kata. Dilengkapi simulasi suara ketukan dan kedipan cahaya senter.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🔊 Mode Audio via Web Audio API</li>
							<li>💡 Mode Flash Cahaya Visual</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/morse" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon semaphore-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<circle cx="12" cy="6" r="3"/>
								<line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="17"/>
								<line x1="12" y1="11" x2="6" y2="8"/>
								<line x1="12" y1="11" x2="18" y2="8"/>
								<line x1="12" y1="17" x2="9" y2="22"/>
								<line x1="12" y1="17" x2="15" y2="22"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag medium">Sedang</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Semaphore (Sinyal Bendera)</h3>
						<p>Tebak huruf atau kata berdasarkan visualisasi posisi bendera Semaphore yang digambar dengan SVG akurat.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🚩 Render Visual SVG Akurat</li>
							<li>🧩 Kuis Tebak Kata & Huruf</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/semaphore" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon sandi-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
								<path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag hard">Sulit</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Sandi (Pecah Sandi)</h3>
						<p>Pecahkan sandi-sandi klasik Pramuka: Kotak I & II, AN/AZ, Koordinat Merah Putih, dan Sandi Rumput.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>📦 Sandi Kotak I & II (SVG)</li>
							<li>🌾 Sandi Rumput & Koordinat</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/sandi" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>

			<!-- Kelompok 2: Teknik Kepramukaan -->
			<div class="cat-group-header">
				<div class="cat-group-icon teknik-group">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3>Teknik Kepramukaan</h3>
					<span class="cat-group-count">9 modul</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="categories-grid">
				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon simpul-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<path d="M5 12c0-2.5 2-4 4-4s4 1.5 4 4-2 4-4 4"/>
								<path d="M13 12c0-2.5 2-4 4-4"/>
								<path d="M3 12h2M19 12h2"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag medium">Tali Temali</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Simpul &amp; Ikatan</h3>
						<p>Uji kemampuan tali temali: simpul mati, anyam, tiang, pangkal, delapan, serta ikatan segi empat, silang, dan kaki tiga.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🪢 Gambar Simpul dari Wikimedia Commons</li>
							<li>📖 30 Soal Bank Acak per Sesi</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/simpul" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon pionir-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<line x1="4" y1="20" x2="20" y2="4"/>
								<line x1="4" y1="4" x2="4" y2="20"/>
								<line x1="20" y1="4" x2="20" y2="20"/>
								<line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag medium">Teknik Pioniring</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Pioniring</h3>
						<p>Pelajari konstruksi pioniring: ikatan segi empat, silang, kaki tiga, simpul pangkal &amp; tiang, serta membangun jembatan, menara, dan tandu dari tongkat.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🪵 Ikatan Segi Empat, Silang &amp; Kaki Tiga</li>
							<li>🏗️ 30 Soal Bank Acak per Sesi</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/pioniring" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon p3k-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag hard">Pertolongan Pertama</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis P3K</h3>
						<p>Kuasai teknik pertolongan pertama: perdarahan, luka bakar, patah tulang, syok, RJP, tersedak, gigitan ular, dan hipotermia.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🩺 Protokol DR-ABC &amp; RICE</li>
							<li>❤️‍🩹 30 Soal Bank Acak per Sesi</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/p3k" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon kompas-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
								<polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag medium">Navigasi</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Kompas &amp; Navigasi</h3>
						<p>Kuasai arah mata angin, cara membaca kompas, azimuth, back azimuth, peta topografi, garis kontur, skala peta, dan teknik resection.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🧭 Tabel Referensi 8 Arah &amp; Derajat</li>
							<li>🗺️ 30 Soal Bank Acak per Sesi</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/kompas" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon kemah-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<path d="M3 17h18M5 17L12 5l7 12"/>
								<path d="M10 17v-4"/>
								<path d="M14 17v-4"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag medium">Teknik Berkemah</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Perkemahan</h3>
						<p>Kuasai teknik mendirikan tenda, bivak alam, api unggun, sanitasi lapangan, survival, sinyal darurat, dan etika Leave No Trace.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>⛺ Prosedur STOP &amp; Sinyal SOS</li>
							<li>🏕️ 30 Soal Bank Acak per Sesi</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/perkemahan" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon pbb-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<line x1="8" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/>
								<line x1="8" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/>
								<line x1="8" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/>
								<line x1="3" y1="6" x2="3.01" y2="6"/>
								<line x1="3" y1="12" x2="3.01" y2="12"/>
								<line x1="3" y1="18" x2="3.01" y2="18"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag medium">Baris-Berbaris</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Baris-Berbaris (PBB)</h3>
						<p>Latih pengetahuan PBB: jenis aba-aba, formasi bershaf &amp; berbanjar, langkah baris, gerakan hadap, penghormatan, dan istilah PBB.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🪖 Referensi Langkah &amp; Formasi Barisan</li>
							<li>🎖️ 30 Soal Bank Acak per Sesi</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/baris-berbaris" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon survival-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<path d="M3 17h18M5 17L12 3l7 14"/>
								<path d="M12 3v6"/>
								<circle cx="12" cy="11" r="1" fill="currentColor"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag hard">Bertahan Hidup</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Survival &amp; Teknik Bertahan</h3>
						<p>Kuasai teknik bertahan hidup: akronim STOP &amp; SURVIVAL, membuat bivak, mendapatkan air dan makanan dari alam, membuat api, serta mengatasi gangguan binatang.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🏕️ Akronim STOP &amp; SURVIVAL</li>
							<li>🌿 30 Soal Bank Acak per Sesi</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/survival" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon flora-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<path d="M12 22V8"/>
								<path d="M5 12H2a10 10 0 0 0 10-10v0a10 10 0 0 0 10 10h-3"/>
								<path d="M8 17a5 5 0 0 1 4-5 5 5 0 0 1 4 5"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag easy">Mudah – Sulit</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Flora &amp; Fauna</h3>
						<p>Kenali tanaman obat, tanaman beracun, flora hutan, jejak hewan, dan hewan berbahaya di alam Indonesia. Dilengkapi gambar dari Wikipedia.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🌿 Tanaman Obat &amp; Beracun + Gambar</li>
							<li>🦎 Jejak Hewan &amp; Hewan Berbahaya</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/flora-fauna" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon siaga-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/>
								<path d="M12 7v5l3 3"/>
								<path d="M9 3.6A9 9 0 0 1 21 12"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag medium">Regulasi</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Pramuka Siaga</h3>
						<p>Uji pemahaman tentang ketentuan Pramuka Siaga: Dwisatya, Dwidarma, SKU Mula–Bantu–Tata, satuan Barung &amp; Perindukan — berdasarkan UU, AD/ART, dan Jukran resmi.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🟢 Dwisatya &amp; Dwidarma</li>
							<li>⭐ 30 Soal Berbasis UU &amp; AD/ART</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/siaga" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Kelompok 3: Pengetahuan Pramuka -->
			<div class="cat-group-header">
				<div class="cat-group-icon penget-group">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3>Pengetahuan Pramuka</h3>
					<span class="cat-group-count">6 modul</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="categories-grid">
				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon sejarah-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
								<polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag medium">Sejarah</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis Sejarah Kepramukaan</h3>
						<p>Pelajari sejarah Baden Powell, perkemahan Brownsea Island, berdirinya Gerakan Pramuka Indonesia 1961, tokoh, dan kode kehormatan.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>🕰️ Linimasa Kepramukaan Dunia &amp; RI</li>
							<li>🧭 30 Soal Bank Acak per Sesi</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/sejarah" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category-card glass-card">
					<div class="card-top">
						<div class="cat-icon uu-bg">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<span class="diff-tag medium">Hukum Pramuka</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3>Kuis UU No. 12 Tahun 2010</h3>
						<p>Uji pemahamanmu tentang Undang-Undang Gerakan Pramuka — asas, tujuan, keanggotaan, kwartir, dan pendidikan kepramukaan.</p>
						<ul class="feature-list">
							<li>📜 30 Soal Bank Acak per Sesi</li>
							<li>⚖️ Penjelasan Pasal di Setiap Soal</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="card-footer">
						<a href="/uu-pramuka" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Mulai Latihan</a>
					</div>
